# Flutter-generated platform glue. These are recreated on every
# `flutter pub get` / `flutter run` from pubspec + native code; tracking
# them produces noisy diffs and merge conflicts. The Gradle wrapper
# (gradlew, gradlew.bat, gradle-wrapper.jar) is deliberately NOT in
# this list — those scripts must stay committed so a fresh checkout
# can build without a system-wide Gradle install.
**/GeneratedPluginRegistrant.java
**/GeneratedPluginRegistrant.h
**/GeneratedPluginRegistrant.m
ios/Flutter/Generated.xcconfig
ios/Flutter/ephemeral/
ios/Flutter/flutter_export_environment.sh

# Env / secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
